<div class="article-info"><span class="byline "><span class="author_name">By <a href="/author/heather-dockray/">Heather Dockray</a></span><time datetime="Tue, 12 Jun 2018 09:27:00 +0000">2018-06-12 09:27:00 UTC</time></span></div>

</header>
<section class='article-content blueprint'>

<p>Most people wouldn't use an international nuclear weapons summit to try out their latest comedy material.</p>
<p>Most people aren't President Trump.</p>
<p>At lunchtime during Trump's Singapore summit Tuesday, the president joked to photographers that they should make him and Kim Jong-un look "handsome and thin."</p>
<div class="see-also"><p class="see-also-link">SEE ALSO: <a href="https://mashable.com/2018/06/07/how-to-talk-to-kids-about-pride-lgbtq-identity/">5 ways parents can talk to kids about LGBTQ identity</a></p></div>
<p>“Getting a good picture everybody? So we look nice and handsome and thin? Perfect,” Trump joked.</p>
<p>Watch the North Korean leader's reaction:</p>
<div class="twitter-wrapper sort-rerender"><div><blockquote class="twitter-tweet">
<p lang="en" dir="ltr">Watch Kim Jong Un's reaction to Trump's joke during the lunch of the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TrumpKimSummit?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" target="_blank">#TrumpKimSummit</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/tictocnews?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" target="_blank">#tictocnews</a> <a href="https://t.co/MtCk4EZ4lJ" target="_blank">https://t.co/MtCk4EZ4lJ</a> <a href="https://t.co/2yCnZDkF8u" target="_blank">pic.twitter.com/2yCnZDkF8u</a></p>
<p>— TicToc by Bloomberg (@tictoc) <a href="https://twitter.com/tictoc/status/1006441820312752128?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" target="_blank">June 12, 2018</a></p>
</blockquote></div></div>
<p>Translators are available on the summit, so it doesn't appear that Kim Jong-un missed the joke. In the past, Trump has called the North Korean leader "short and fat" in a tweet.</p>
<div class="twitter-wrapper sort-rerender"><div><blockquote class="twitter-tweet">
<p lang="en" dir="ltr">Why would Kim Jong-un insult me by calling me "old," when I would NEVER call him "short and fat?" Oh well, I try so hard to be his friend - and maybe someday that will happen!</p>
<p>— Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) <a href="https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/929511061954297857?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" target="_blank">November 12, 2017</a></p>
</blockquote></div></div>
<p>In other words ... I never thought I would have anything in common with a <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/11/world/asia/north-korea-human-rights.html" target="_blank">spectacularly violent</a>, brutally oppressive North Korean dictator who starves his own people, but I was glad we could share this join moment of horror together.</p>
<p>Progress, people!</p>
